Package: DataGenomics
Type: LearnGenViz
Title: Comprehensive Toolkit for Genomic Data Visualization and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Loukas Theodosiou, PhD
Maintainer: Loukas Theodosiou <theodosiou@evolbio.mpg.de>
Description: DataGenomics provides a robust set of tools for visualizing and analyzing genomic data. 
    The package integrates powerful plotting libraries and bioinformatics tools, making it suitable 
    for various applications such as sequence analysis, phylogenetic tree construction, 
    network visualization, and statistical modeling. It streamlines the analysis process 
    for genomics and related biological research, helping researchers generate complex plots, 
    analyze sequence alignments, and work with phylogenetic and multivariate data effortlessly.
